Body:
with get_eel_server('examples/06 - jinja_templates/hello.py',
    'templates/hello.html') as eel_url:
    driver.get(eel_url)
    assert driver.title == 'Hello, World!'
    driver.find_element_by_css_selector('a').click()
    WebDriverWait(driver, 2.0).until(expected_conditions.
        presence_of_element_located((By.XPATH,
        '//h1[text()="This is page 2"]')))
